  "description" : "* Based on a seinen manga written by http://anidb.net/cr55229 [Akasaka Aka] and drawn by http://anidb.net/cr40028 [Yokoyari Mengo].\nThe story enters a new stage... Six months have passed since the release of \"POP IN 2.\" Thanks to http://anidb.net/ch131353 [MEM-cho]`s efforts, B-Komachi is now on the verge of a breakthrough. http://anidb.net/ch128518 [Aqua] is steadily progressing as a multi-talented artist and http://anidb.net/ch131354 [Akane] is on her way to becoming a skilled actress. Meanwhile, http://anidb.net/ch130523 [Kana] has lost her former cheerful demeanor. And http://anidb.net/ch128520 [Ruby] is climbing the ranks of the entertainment industry while pursuing the truth behind the deaths of http://anidb.net/ch127016 [Ai] and http://anidb.net/ch128521 [Gorou] — using lies as a weapon.\nSource: HIDIVE\nNote: The first episode received an early screening at a special event on 28 December 2025 at Marunouchi Piccadilly in Tokyo and 104 additional venues across Japan. The regular TV broadcast started on 14 January 2026.",
